&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="2-include-parent-properties">2. Include Parent Properties&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>When fetching notes, consider including parent properties for context:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Troubleshooting</title><link>/docs/overview/troubleshooting/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/overview/troubleshooting/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="common-issues">Common Issues&lt;/h3>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Database Locked Errors&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>The API will retry automatically&lt;/li>
&lt;li>If persistent, check for long-running transactions&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Property Not Found&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Properties are extracted from content automatically&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Check that your content uses the correct syntax: &lt;code>{key::value}&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Search Not Working&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Ensure search terms are properly URL-encoded&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Check that the content contains the search terms&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Template Processing Errors&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Verify template syntax&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Check that placeholder names are valid&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h3 id="debug-mode">Debug Mode&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>Enable debug logging by checking the server logs for detailed error information.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Changelog</title><link>/docs/overview/changelog/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>/docs/overview/changelog/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="version-100">Version 1.0.0&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Initial API release&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Full CRUD operations for pages and notes&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Property system with pattern matching&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Full-text search capabilities&lt;/li>
&lt;li>File attachment support&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Template system&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Webhook notifications&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Batch operations for efficiency&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item></channel></rss>